Title: Omron HEM-7200-AP3(JPN1) Bp Monitor
Description: Keep a check on your blood pressure by regularly monitoring it with this automatic BP monitor from Omron. Wide Pressure Range This BP monitor measures the pressure from 0 to 299 mmHg and displays accurate values of systolic and diastolic pressures. High Accuracy The Omron BP monitor ensures accurate readings by detecting body movements. Memory Function The memory function stores the last three readings taken within the last 10 minutes and the unit displays their average on the LCD display. Pulse Measurement The LCD display shows the pulse rate ranging from 40 to 180 beats/minute. This unit also detects irregular heartbeat.

Title: Juvenile Hair Building Fiber Refill Bag Of Dark Brown
Description: Juvenile Hair Fibers gives the fuller head of hairs in just 30 seconds. It merge with your own hair to add real volume, allowing style like you never again thought possible. Every time you look into in the mirror you will be amazed by the natural results that are virtually undetectable to the naked eye. Juvenile Hair Building Fiber is made up of 100% Natural cotton fibers which binds to your hairs all day through wind, rain and perspiration. Juvenile Hair Building Fibers are the perfect solution for both men and women suffering with hair loss and thinning hair who want to change the way they feel about their appearance. Balding and thinning areas instantly vanish leaving you with a natural looking full head of hair. Juvenile Hair Building Fiber refill bag can be used in any regular fiber bottle.How to use: Open the refill bag of Juvenile Hair Building Fiber, pour the fiber into Juvenile Hair Building Fiber or any hair fiber bottle or sprinkler bottle. For men and women, clean your hair dry and style hair as usual, shake and sprinkle the fiber equally into the thinning areas, gently pat your hair to disperse fibers. It works on sweat at the gym or when you go for a run or in the light rain. Juvenile hair fibers will not leak as dye onto your skin.

Title: Nanogen Thickening Hair Fibres Medium Brown - Pack of 2
Description: Imagine if you never had to worry about the appearance of thinning hair again? You can regain that great feeling of confidence you had years ago when a full head of hair was something you took for granted!Easy to Apply: -Nanogen Fibres are applied quickly and without mess by simply shaking the unique container over thin or thinning hair. This releases thousands of microscopic colour-matched hair fibres, which bind electrostatically to, and branch off of, each individual hair. Charged with static electricity, they bond to your own hair in fir-tree patterns, creating a natural looking and natural feeling density. Nanogen Fibres bond to your hair so securely they will stay in place all day, and will not stain or smear. Nanogen Fibres will even resist strong winds, rain, and swimming when combined with Nanogen Fibre Locking Spray.Undetectable, Natural Appearance:- Nanogen Fibres actually merge with your own hair, adding real volume, allowing styling like you never again thought possible. Every time you look in the mirror you will be truly amazed by the natural results that are virtually undetectable to the naked eye. You can even build up the amount of Nanogen Fibres you use over time to create a gradual transformation. Nanogen Fibres can also be used before hair transplants to subtly build up the appearance of thicker hair so the transplants don’t cause an obvious and sudden change. Not only do Nanogen Fibres look natural, the container is elegant and discreetly makes no mention of hair camouflage at all.Patent Pending Technology:- Nanogen Fibres benefit from a patent pending Electrostatic Coating and Electrostatic Strip. These innovations intensify the hair thickening effect created by Nanogen Fibres. Nanogen Fibres have been independently proven to create unrivalled hair density you can really see. The Nanogen Fibres jar also has fill-level windows to indicate when you are running low, to ensure you never run out.100% Safe for Male and Female Thinning Hair :- Over 1 million incredible transformations prove that Nanogen Fibres are safe. They are completely natural and they will not damage your hair or scalp. That’s why they are used by leading hair transplant surgeons to conceal thinning hair right up to surgery, and afterwards to hide the healing wounds. Nanogen Fibres are recommended by the Alopecia Society for men and women with thinning hair. Hazards and Cautions :- For external use only, Avoid contact with eyes, In case of irritation cease use.Ingredients:- Natural Keratin, Electrostatic Coating, Colour Lock System

Description: Bio Fresh Rose Oil of Bulgaria Day Cream with Multi Active, Age Control - 50 ml:Rose products are from the NATURAL roses of Rose Valley in Bulgaria-Kazanlak, extracted from the "Rosa Damascena " by steam distillation. Production of rose and rose oil in Bulgaria-Kazanlak has started 16th century and today the region is the biggest rose oil exporter. Around 4000 kg of fresh roses distilled to get just 1 kg of high quality rose oil.There are two main Rose Oil types; Rose ottos are extracted through steam distillation, while rose absolutes are obtained through solvent extraction or supercritical carbon dioxide extraction, with the absolute being used more commonly in perfumery.
